name: BADNEWS//GOODNEWS
description:
BADNEWS//GOODNEWS is a representation of all things chaotic, brutal, glorious, astonishing and misshapen in the form of an all-seeing eye. It portrays my view of the world in the past up until the general present, all the better and the worse things in life, and the expectations and fear of the future.

1000 x 1150 PX
mix digital media, done in autodesk maya, keyshot, photoshop & premiere.
